![Front Panel Diagram](../assets/front-panel-diagram.svg)

### Front Panel Controls

| Control | Function |
|---------|----------|
| **POWER** | Main power button (press to toggle on/off) |
| **VOLTAGE** | Rotary encoder to adjust output voltage |
| **CURRENT** | Rotary encoder to adjust current limit |
| **OUTPUT** | Enable/disable output (green = on, red/off = disabled) |
| **MENU** | Access configuration menu system |
| **← →** | Navigation buttons (menu navigation) |
| **ENTER** | Confirm menu selections |

### Front Panel Display

| Display Element | Shows |
|-----------------|-------|
| **Main Display** | Large 4-digit voltage and current values |
| **Mode Indicator** | CV (constant voltage) or CC (constant current) |
| **Status Icons** | OVP, OCP, OTP status indicators |
| **Menu Area** | Menu navigation when in menu mode |
